          "statusText": "In late 2024, GTA and Transportation staff completed the GoBORO transit mobility study, recommending significant route/frequency changes. The City's first 15-minute-service route, CrossMax Purple, launched March 2024 and averages 10,000 riders/week — a ~54% ridership increase over the routes it replaced.",
